children.characters: Combine Figma with your favorite CMS and ship websites in 5 minutes.

children.name: Components and block
children.characters: Components and blocks are fixed to the common and popular 12 Grid system, something designers and developers can agree on.

children.name: We havent forgotten
children.characters: We havent forgotten about responsive layout. With Startup Framework, you can create a website with full mobile support.

children.name: Samples will show yo
children.characters: Samples will show you the feeling on how to play around using the components in the website building process.

children.name: You can decide wheth
children.characters: You can decide whether to create your site using UI Kit blocks or samples. The blocks can merge together in various combinations.

children.name: The most important p
children.characters: The most important part of the luisa.cloud is the samples. The samples form a set of 25 usable pages you can use as is or you can add new blocks from UI Kit. By choosing one of the 25 configurations of the future startup, the process of creation is simple and easy.

children.name: Startup Design Frame
children.characters: luisa.cloud contains components which can easily be inte-grated into almost any design.

children.name: The Generator App is
children.characters: The Generator App is an online tool that helps you to export ready-made templates ready to work as your future website. It helps you to combine slides, panels and other components and export it as a set of static files: HTML/CSS/JS.

children.name: A high-quality solut
children.characters: Simply design your blog or website with your favorite tool. Dont think about coding!

children.name: Youre buying an acc
children.characters: Youre buying an access to the luisa.cloud app to export ready-made templates with the rest source files included. Its an online tool, not a software. For more details about generators workflow watch this tutorial.
